1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 d6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Qxd4 Nc6 5. Bb5 Bd7 6. Bxc6 {This is the main 
line.} Bxc6 7. c4 Nf6 8. Nc3 g6 9. O-O Bg7 10. Qd3 O-O {Black has good 
development and wil. try to undermine white's very solid maroczy bind.} 11. Nd4 
Rc8 *

